<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٥٧٢٢ - حَدَّثَنَا ابْنُ فُضَيْلٍ، عَنْ لَيْثٍ، عَنِ ابْنِ الْأَسْوَدِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِنَّ مِنْ تَمَامِ التَّحِيَّةِ الْمُصَافَحَةَ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>